last_episode_to_air.overview: The renegade physician William P. Rush, a discreet, highly expensive "medical fixer" for L.A.'s elite, is in the path of an old flame.

name: Rush
overview: Doctor William Rush is not your average on-call professional. He's not attached to any hospital, he's highly discreet -- no matter the ailment, his clients must pay a cash-only premium, and the doctor can party with the best of them. Dr. Rush has no desire to change his life or how he lives it, until an old flame and his conscience begin to stir things up.
